729967f-a.title: Richmond: York Avenue - Prospect Avenue
729967f-a.text:
York Avenue, west side, about 250 feet north of
Prospect Avenue, showing the Pat Smith Club. TThis building
was until 1930 the German Lutheran Ciurch.
July 2, 1932
P. L. Sperr

729966f-a.title: Richmond: York Avenue - Pauw Street
729966f-a.text:
271 (left) and 273 York Avenue, east side, between
Pauw and Arnold Streets. The two houses are frame dwellings
with stucco fronts; number 271 appears on Beers's 1874 map.
July 21, 1932
P. L. Sperr
